[
    {
        "text": "When you invest in a stock,...",
        "startTime": 497,
        "endTime": 1901,
        "slowStartTime": 895,
        "slowEndTime": 3076
    },
    {
        "text": "...you're taking a risk that the value may go down rather than up.",
        "startTime": 2139,
        "endTime": 5739,
        "slowStartTime": 3358,
        "slowEndTime": 8833
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, we get it.",
        "startTime": 6289,
        "endTime": 7481,
        "slowStartTime": 9583,
        "slowEndTime": 11447
    },
    {
        "text": "Investing can be risky.",
        "startTime": 7711,
        "endTime": 8985,
        "slowStartTime": 11717,
        "slowEndTime": 13703
    },
    {
        "text": "One way to manage that risk is to learn about asset allocation and diversification.",
        "startTime": 9320,
        "endTime": 14211,
        "slowStartTime": 14130,
        "slowEndTime": 21541
    },
    {
        "text": "Asset allocation is financial lingo for how you distribute your money...",
        "startTime": 14585,
        "endTime": 18439,
        "slowStartTime": 22028,
        "slowEndTime": 27884
    },
    {
        "text": "...across types of investment like the strategic decision...",
        "startTime": 18647,
        "endTime": 21501,
        "slowStartTime": 28121,
        "slowEndTime": 32476
    },
    {
        "text": "...of which baskets to put your eggs in and how many.",
        "startTime": 21595,
        "endTime": 24559,
        "slowStartTime": 32543,
        "slowEndTime": 37064
    },
    {
        "text": "The different baskets are called asset classes.",
        "startTime": 24781,
        "endTime": 27422,
        "slowStartTime": 37321,
        "slowEndTime": 41358
    },
    {
        "text": "To help you decide where to put your eggs,...",
        "startTime": 27666,
        "endTime": 29445,
        "slowStartTime": 41649,
        "slowEndTime": 44392
    },
    {
        "text": "...ask yourself how much time do you have before you need to use your money,...",
        "startTime": 29676,
        "endTime": 33036,
        "slowStartTime": 44664,
        "slowEndTime": 49779
    },
    {
        "text": "...how comfortable are you with risk, and how does your current financial situation look.",
        "startTime": 33313,
        "endTime": 37703,
        "slowStartTime": 50120,
        "slowEndTime": 56780
    },
    {
        "text": "Diversification is about strategically putting the right mix of different eggs...",
        "startTime": 38127,
        "endTime": 42590,
        "slowStartTime": 57340,
        "slowEndTime": 64110
    },
    {
        "text": "...in each of your baskets.",
        "startTime": 42751,
        "endTime": 43896,
        "slowStartTime": 64276,
        "slowEndTime": 66069
    },
    {
        "text": "The key is that you shouldn't invest all your money in one company,...",
        "startTime": 44143,
        "endTime": 47131,
        "slowStartTime": 66364,
        "slowEndTime": 70922
    },
    {
        "text": "...one industry, one country, one anything.",
        "startTime": 47371,
        "endTime": 50014,
        "slowStartTime": 71207,
        "slowEndTime": 75246
    },
    {
        "text": "Ideally, you want your investments to be negatively correlated,...",
        "startTime": 50299,
        "endTime": 53495,
        "slowStartTime": 75599,
        "slowEndTime": 80468
    },
    {
        "text": "...so when one is going down, another is going up.",
        "startTime": 53646,
        "endTime": 56290,
        "slowStartTime": 80619,
        "slowEndTime": 84660
    },
    {
        "text": "Here are some typical ways to diversify your portfolio:...",
        "startTime": 56843,
        "endTime": 59449,
        "slowStartTime": 85415,
        "slowEndTime": 89398
    },
    {
        "text": "...invest in companies in different countries,...",
        "startTime": 59807,
        "endTime": 62245,
        "slowStartTime": 89861,
        "slowEndTime": 93592
    },
    {
        "text": "...own stock in small and large companies,...",
        "startTime": 62645,
        "endTime": 65655,
        "slowStartTime": 94117,
        "slowEndTime": 98708
    },
    {
        "text": "...and invest in companies in a variety of industries.",
        "startTime": 65786,
        "endTime": 68905,
        "slowStartTime": 98829,
        "slowEndTime": 103583
    },
    {
        "text": "One downside to diversification is...",
        "startTime": 69299,
        "endTime": 71845,
        "slowStartTime": 104098,
        "slowEndTime": 107993
    },
    {
        "text": "...if one of your investments does very well,...",
        "startTime": 72050,
        "endTime": 74194,
        "slowStartTime": 108225,
        "slowEndTime": 111516
    },
    {
        "text": "...you won't make as much as if it was your only investment.",
        "startTime": 74373,
        "endTime": 76829,
        "slowStartTime": 111710,
        "slowEndTime": 115468
    },
    {
        "text": "Conversely, if you owned only one stock...",
        "startTime": 77179,
        "endTime": 79944,
        "slowStartTime": 115919,
        "slowEndTime": 120141
    },
    {
        "text": "...and the company went out of business,...",
        "startTime": 80099,
        "endTime": 81951,
        "slowStartTime": 120299,
        "slowEndTime": 123152
    },
    {
        "text": "...you will lose more money than if you had diversified your money.",
        "startTime": 82146,
        "endTime": 85036,
        "slowStartTime": 123369,
        "slowEndTime": 127779
    },
    {
        "text": "Diversification won't eliminate risk...",
        "startTime": 85299,
        "endTime": 87522,
        "slowStartTime": 128098,
        "slowEndTime": 131508
    },
    {
        "text": "...but it's a smart way to manage risk...",
        "startTime": 87655,
        "endTime": 89715,
        "slowStartTime": 131632,
        "slowEndTime": 134798
    },
    {
        "text": "...while allowing you to build your portfolio.",
        "startTime": 89898,
        "endTime": 92065,
        "slowStartTime": 134997,
        "slowEndTime": 138322
    }
]